Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going through the front door \Nwould be a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, we'll enter through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:57.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(306,529)}#15  A Battle of Legend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that is how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Those were all Noble Phantasms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By comparison, this guy wasn't \Nas tough as he looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I can't stand meat-heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you value your life, stand back, fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is far too early for laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am tired of seeing heroes that do not \Nfall when cut or burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I have never seen a man \Ntruly return from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem your life has been sublimated \Nthrough a Noble Phantasm of heroic tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Noble Phantasm is the one asset I lack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense, I suppose even \NI stand at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although vexing, it seems only the highest \Nclass of arms will work on that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is said Heracles overcame twelve penances,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and was welcomed by the gods afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He is unyielding,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the ultimate expression of human perseverance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My treasury, however, is the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is infinite, the ultimate expression \Nof overwhelming force.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, it overflows with \Nweaponry to slay heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing at being a nursemaid, Heracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me in earnest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or you will use up all your labors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker won't lose to anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's the strongest in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Kiri—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother was destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Killed at the hands of the man \Nshe loved above all others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother said that she would \Nbecome the Holy Grail,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Kiritsugu would keep her safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were... We were betrayed by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And cast aside like some tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying... You're lying. \NThat must be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you're saying has to be a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Kiritsugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay... I can manage on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say that he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the traitor died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say he thought only of himself until his end,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never even coming back for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to live my life by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it does have to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because he had a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That man had a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A family other than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A family? My little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know you'll be able to kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to kill each other soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the Greater Grail's \Nflame was not extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The battle ended without resolution, \Nso it will soon resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait, Illyasviel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That gives you a reason to live, \Njust like that human, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why does my body have to be \Nopened up every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They should just quit the stupid Holy Grail War...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it is our purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The miracle that occurred a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were created in order to replicate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity's salvation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That will only bring happiness to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are we living for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have no concept of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because we are just tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are the ones used, not the users.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even Elder Acht has probably \Nnever experienced joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We are all nothing but tools \Nto activate the Holy Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To that end, we have suffered \Nfor a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then, they finally achieved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Achieved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are the Einzberns' \Ncrowning achievement,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the end result of the techniques that created us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much time passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they will never be able to create \None that surpasses you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if you are defeated, they will all give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Acht will probably turn \Noff the power source himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because they will have their answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That we are relics of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all end your own lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the factory called the Einzberns
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will abandon their millennial research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With a smile on their faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,saying they gave it their best, \Nbut it was all for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're all alive! Why do you have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't I be the only one to die, \Nthe one who's gonna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not mourn us, sweet child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if everything was futile, we do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we cannot be saved, we will \Nfinally be freed of our obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Duty, duty... It's always duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do the Einzberns think they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We never had identities of our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sella, and starting today, \NI will be looking after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Leysritt, who has been \Nassigned to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Illya... Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive her. Leysritt's link \Nis not yet complete—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Making introductions is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're all the same, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then is the Servant here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:11:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the summoning has already been performed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He is the great hero renowned in \NGreek myth, Heracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How awe-inspiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rejoice, mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With a Heroic Spirit such as this summoned, \Nyour victory is assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We place our lives and our \Nmeager abilities at your—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Servants are nothing more than tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's on the inside doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can manage just fine on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win the Holy Grail War by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need Berserker...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker will keep you safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Servants are just familiars \Nthat are bound by rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If not for my Command Seals, \Nit would betray me in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin linking you to Berserker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seventy percent of your body is \Ncomposed of Magic Circuits,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you will receive far more Servant \Nfeedback than an ordinary Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please exercise the utmost caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Illya, if it hurts, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter. Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? \NMove like I said, Berserker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Move, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself the most \Npowerful Heroic Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please sever the link!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's perform the pact ritual another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll break him soon enough, so be quiet and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the most powerful Master in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right... I was in the middle of the final test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I make it back to the castle alive, \NI can go to Fuyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I left Berserker behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I get back to the castle, I'll just \Nsummon a new Servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll summon one that won't cause \Nme pain and isn't so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I left you behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you don't want to make me suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you don't want to hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get them, Berserker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't protect me because I ordered \Nyou to or because you're a Servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been protecting me of your \Nown free will, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so strong, Berserker...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.18,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:48.77,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker won't lose to the likes of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.93,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because Berserker is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's stronger than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:15:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have no way to fight them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to save people,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,save yourself first, and then think about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your defeat is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Since you will die anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,why not lay down your burden at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting unencumbered, you still \Nhave a chance of slaying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then die with your mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I shall give you the greatest of labors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes eleven!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've run out of chances, Heracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Had he forsaken his mistress at once, \Nhe would have stood a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, he was no more than a lowly \Nbeast? One who lived to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had hoped for better from a fellow demigod.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did not take you to be such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Return to me, Berserker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I told you to come back \Ninside me, so why won't—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No use, little puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Chains of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything bound in these chains \Ncannot escape, not even a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it binds those with high divinity levels, \Nsuch as this man, more tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As if I would allow him to teleport \Naway via Command Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Berserker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? I can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all dark. I can't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay here with me forever, Berserker...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Troublesome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You surpass your own myth to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if everything's dark, I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're strong, Berserker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With you next to me like this, \NI don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you always protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might have been scary, \Nbut actually, you were kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were big, just like Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted you to scoop me \Nup in your arms, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does betrayal rub you the wrong way?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caster's head must be hurting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're already messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have the will to fight, \Nbut that means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It just pisses me off that there are Servants like you!
